## DETECTION METHODS (AI/CCTV)

**Computer Vision Models Required**:
- PPE Detection (helmet, gloves, uniform, safety shoes)
- Smoking Detection
- Fire/Smoke Detection
- Nozzle Tampering Detection (anomaly detection)
- Queue Length Estimation
- Occupancy Monitoring (restricted zones)
- License Plate Recognition (tanker verification)
- Spill Detection (liquid on ground)
- Personnel Identification (unauthorized access)
- Activity Recognition (tanker unloading procedures, handwashing)

**Integration Requirements**:
- ATG System API (tank levels, density, temperature)
- DU Calibration Logs (fuel dispensing accuracy)
- POS System (billing, payment data)
- Certificate Management System (license expiry tracking)
- Biometric Attendance System
- Fire Panel Integration (alarm status)

